1216
00:52:32,536 --> 00:52:36,999
on a massive PSD that doesn't have any bounds to it, really,

1217
00:52:37,780 --> 00:52:39,161
and see where it takes me.

1218
00:52:39,521 --> 00:52:41,002
And one of the reasons for that in this case

1219
00:52:41,042 --> 00:52:41,543
is because the,

1220
00:52:43,415 --> 00:52:45,496
The key art that we make, and I left this out of the talk,

1221
00:52:45,516 --> 00:52:49,538
but there are a lot of actual format and crop specifications

1222
00:52:49,558 --> 00:52:50,398
that I have to hit.

1223
00:52:50,759 --> 00:52:51,919
And what that means is that I have

1224
00:52:51,959 --> 00:52:54,640
to build a lot of margin area into every illustration

1225
00:52:54,661 --> 00:52:55,121
that we do.

1226
00:52:55,581 --> 00:52:59,963
