1233
00:53:15,837 --> 00:53:18,359
there is a sort of paralysis in the early phases

1234
00:53:18,419 --> 00:53:19,320
of doing a concept.

1235
00:53:19,420 --> 00:53:21,882
I'm not sure if you ever feel like you might be

1236
00:53:21,902 --> 00:53:24,384
getting ahead of those requirements or desirements,

