00:53:43,636 --> 00:53:51,340
say is, I think maybe I would rephrase your question as, am I ever concerned that the

1247
00:53:51,380 --> 00:53:55,582
people who see my artwork internally will make a judgment on the quality of the composition

1248
00:53:55,602 --> 00:53:59,023
I'm developing before I really get to a point where it's fully been expressed?

1249
00:53:59,750 --> 00:54:01,371
